It's been two years since we have re-opened. It has been the toughest, most challenging time every Cast Member has experienced for many reasons. As things hopefully start to get better, times have changed, and life has changed, but the support between Cast Members has become stronger than ever. Thanks for being there for one another.

And honestly, if you weren't for you guys... I don't know where my mental as well as physical health would be...

Sushi Damu in Tustin is the best AYCE sushi place in the OC! 

With wonderful service and premium quality sushi, you have so many awesome items to choose from! From appetizers, nigiri, rolls, hand rolls, an option to upgrade to sashimi, and incredible drinks and cocktails, this will be your go-to sushi place! 

We enjoyed amazing nigiri, beautiful cut sashimi, a Dragon Breath Roll, hand rolls, a lychee martini, a watermelon frose, and a dragonfruit mojito! 

Thank you for the invite Sushi Damu! We can't wait to come back!

How to order my favorite Starbucks hack:
1. Order an apple juice to the top of the line of whatever size drink you order 
2. Add pumpkin spice (1.5 pumps for a tall, 2 pumps for a grande and 3 pumps for a venti) 
3. Fill the rest with ice
4. Give your drink a quick swirl and enioy!!!
